<div class="_j_content_box">
	        <div data-seq="262737540" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">写在前面</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261729843">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;可能是离得比较近，笔者去十三陵的次数一个手已经数不清过来了。每个陵都亲自去过，也曾拍过很多不同的照片。十三陵没有故宫的富丽堂皇，也没有什刹海的锦绣华灯，只有寥寥几座古迹和绵延的群山。冬日里若是树叶凋枯，荒草丛生，在这还能寻到一丝凄凉。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261918977" data-seq="261918978" data-pid="261918977" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261918977.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6D/26/wKgBZ1n5t5-AI7xmABEMc_WiOW489.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6D/26/wKgBZ1n5t5-AI7xmABEMc_WiOW489.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261918977" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262555395">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;明朝是一个很特殊的王朝，不和亲、不纳贡、不赔款、不割地，既有天子守国门，君王死社稷的大义凛然，也有于谦、海瑞、戚继光、张居正、邢玠那样的高风亮节。每次在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>周边看到雄关万丈的长城，笔者总能想起这个“社稷为重，君为轻”的王朝。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_263863853" data-seq="263863854" data-pid="263863853" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/263863853.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/08/6A/wKgBZ1oCkVeAMoS8AAdtOVI0qKQ19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/08/6A/wKgBZ1oCkVeAMoS8AAdtOVI0qKQ19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="263863853" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="263863015">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;明朝一共有十六位皇帝，十三位葬在了十三陵。明太祖朱元璋葬在了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南京" target="_blank">南京</a>，建文帝朱允炆下落不明，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62859.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="景泰" target="_blank">景泰</a>帝朱祁钰死后被废，葬在了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13541.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="房山" target="_blank">房山</a>，也就是《女医明妃传》里的弟弟。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261980905" data-seq="261980906" data-pid="261980905" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261980905.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A4/6F/wKgBZ1n543OAS4e5AAhsTCTYy2885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A4/6F/wKgBZ1n543OAS4e5AAhsTCTYy2885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261980905" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="263824731">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;先说说建文帝朱允炆。大儿子先死，朱元璋直接把皇位传给了自己的长孙朱允炆，把自己剩余的几个儿子都打发到外地，封为了藩王。朱允炆登基后，听从大臣建议，削了几位叔叔的藩，仅留了一个最棘手的四叔，燕王朱棣。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262586157" data-seq="262586158" data-pid="262586157" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262586157.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:468px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4E/90/wKgBZ1n8szqAUbnVAAOkL_u707s55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4E/90/wKgBZ1n8szqAUbnVAAOkL_u707s55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262586157" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264701859">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;建文帝派三十万大军围剿，朱棣奉天靖难，举兵南下。一路上尽是自己的老友和旧将，队伍也越拉越大，三年就反推到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南京" target="_blank">南京</a>城下。守城大将开门受降，宫内起火，建文帝下落不明(一说是死了，一说是出家了)。这样，燕王朱棣就成为了明朝第三位皇帝，十三陵的历史，就是从他开始的。笔者就按建陵的时间顺序，带你去十三陵走一走。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="262586274" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">大红门、神道</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261918979">
            <br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;进入陵区，最先映入眼帘的是一座六柱五间的石牌坊。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261921199" data-seq="261921200" data-pid="261921199" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261921199.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6E/F5/wKgBZ1n5uaCABkpUAAnkA-6omBA13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6E/F5/wKgBZ1n5uaCABkpUAAnkA-6omBA13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261921199" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261921915">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;过了石牌坊大概500米，就会来到十三陵的正门，以前陵区有围墙，现在只剩一个大红门了。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261921668" data-seq="261921670" data-pid="261921668" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261921668.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6F/49/wKgBZ1n5ugKADz-RAAXJDZGGc7E33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6F/49/wKgBZ1n5ugKADz-RAAXJDZGGc7E33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261921668" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261920806">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大红门的两侧各有一个下马碑，刻有“官员人等在此下马”。其实这个碑还是很常见的，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的国子监、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10432.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="承德" target="_blank">承德</a>的避暑山庄都有这种石碑。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262847468" data-seq="262847469" data-pid="262847468" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:627px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262847468.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:592px;width:627px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/28/wKgBZ1n-EXSAd0SdABAA_PTGdHI855.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/28/wKgBZ1n-EXSAd0SdABAA_PTGdHI855.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262847468" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262847470">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大红门的背面。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261924766" data-seq="261924767" data-pid="261924766" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261924766.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:360px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/71/AF/wKgBZ1n5vJ6AUdt9AAb2oh8GPLk24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/71/AF/wKgBZ1n5vJ6AUdt9AAb2oh8GPLk24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261924766" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261925005">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大红门最先应该是有门的，地上留有门栓。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261924956" data-seq="261924957" data-pid="261924956" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261924956.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:383px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/71/EE/wKgBZ1n5vOWAd902AAdhchKrIoM81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/71/EE/wKgBZ1n5vOWAd902AAdhchKrIoM81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261924956" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261981816">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;神道是明十三陵的入口，主要摆了一些象征皇家威仪的石像、建筑以及歌颂明成祖朱棣的生平事迹的神功圣德碑楼。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261925729" data-seq="261925730" data-pid="261925729" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261925729.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/72/98/wKgBZ1n5vZKADW_qAAtc5g9EePc52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/72/98/wKgBZ1n5vZKADW_qAAtc5g9EePc52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261925729" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261927382">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;神功圣德碑是朱棣<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63863.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="长子" target="_blank">长子</a>朱高炽所写，主要记录了朱棣一生的经历。十三陵中除了思陵都有神功圣德碑，但只有这个是有字的，其他的都是无字碑。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261927187" data-seq="261927188" data-pid="261927187" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261927187.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:849px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/73/BE/wKgBZ1n5vs2ACx2iAArcU1UhpYY26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/73/BE/wKgBZ1n5vs2ACx2iAArcU1UhpYY26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261927187" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_261927318" data-seq="261927319" data-pid="261927318" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261927318.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/73/D9/wKgBZ1n5vwuAGWxFAA_MtZie2ug86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/73/D9/wKgBZ1n5vwuAGWxFAA_MtZie2ug86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261927318" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_263852594" data-seq="263852595" data-pid="263852594" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/263852594.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:552px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/00/5B/wKgBZ1oCgaOAf40PAFIidUmXQUQ966.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/00/5B/wKgBZ1oCgaOAf40PAFIidUmXQUQ966.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="263852594" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div data-seq="261980978" data-index="3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">长陵-明成祖朱棣</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261980907">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;长陵是十三陵的首陵，也是十三陵中最大的陵，不同于其他陵，长陵完整的保留着原有的地面建筑，主人是明朝第三位皇帝朱棣，年号“永乐”。朱元璋靠武力一统天下，年号取为“洪武”。朱棣登基时，天下太平，所以选用“永乐”这个年号。这个皇帝可能有些人会感觉陌生，但要是一说“郑和”这个人，估计无人不晓，这位皇帝就是郑和的“主子”。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262561586" data-seq="262561587" data-pid="262561586" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:268px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262561586.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:347px;width:268px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/40/1B/wKgBZ1n8i6KAZwUCAAAxZoKzijQ15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/40/1B/wKgBZ1n8i6KAZwUCAAAxZoKzijQ15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262561586" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262561588">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;他抢了侄儿的皇位，也诛过方孝孺“十族”，一口气杀了873个人。他确实不是个好人，但他确实是个好皇帝。他&nbsp;在位期间，励精图治，遣郑和七下西洋，迁都<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，编永乐大典，五征漠北，开创永乐盛世。在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城里，但凡有点历史的古建筑，像故宫、天坛、太庙，都是他下令修建的。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261941009" data-seq="261941010" data-pid="261941009" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261941009.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/16/wKgBZ1n5yO2AStBPAAbtAQWhQrA17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/16/wKgBZ1n5yO2AStBPAAbtAQWhQrA17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261941009" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262573278">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;进入陵区大门，依次经过祾恩门，祾恩殿、棂星门就可以来到里面的明楼。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261941403" data-seq="261941404" data-pid="261941403" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261941403.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:337px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/4A/wKgBZ1n5yTCARMaHAAcJpSeUOvI20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/4A/wKgBZ1n5yTCARMaHAAcJpSeUOvI20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261941403" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261944758">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;祾恩这个词是“领恩”的谐音，目的是为了告诫后世子孙前来谒陵时要牢记长辈的恩情。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261944649" data-seq="261944650" data-pid="261944649" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261944649.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/81/D4/wKgBZ1n5y2iAXoywAAekezYkiVo84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/81/D4/wKgBZ1n5y2iAXoywAAekezYkiVo84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261944649" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_261957266" data-seq="261957267" data-pid="261957266" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261957266.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8E/09/wKgBZ1n51CiAaOkKAAohKasoacY14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/8E/09/wKgBZ1n51CiAaOkKAAohKasoacY14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261957266" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_261968219" data-seq="261968220" data-pid="261968219" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261968219.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/96/F6/wKgBZ1n52uyAE3kAAAojtPXWbC432.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/96/F6/wKgBZ1n52uyAE3kAAAojtPXWbC432.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261968219" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261952081">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;过了祾恩门就是祾恩殿。祾恩殿面阔九间、进深五间，象征皇帝的九五之尊。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262575566" data-seq="262575567" data-pid="262575566" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262575566.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/48/32/wKgBZ1n8mwSAXFUEAAtN49SOd4071.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/48/32/wKgBZ1n8mwSAXFUEAAtN49SOd4071.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262575566" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_261955552" data-seq="261955553" data-pid="261955552" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261955552.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/86/6C/wKgBZ1n5zsuAfLpfAAuKi8xLflg10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/86/6C/wKgBZ1n5zsuAfLpfAAuKi8xLflg10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261955552" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261959626">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这个皇帝有多辉煌，其实看看祾恩殿里的柱子有多粗就明白了。60根顶梁柱直径都超过1米，全部为金丝楠木。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_261953694" data-seq="261953695" data-pid="261953694" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/261953694.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:455px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/89/FB/wKgBZ1n50XmAekIBAAbXSzBVlLg36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/89/FB/wKgBZ1n50XmAekIBAAbXSzBVlLg36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="261953694" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261961005">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这么粗金丝楠木到清朝就已经绝迹了，康熙乾隆修陵时都是用的松木。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10432.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="承德" target="_blank">承德</a>避暑山庄里修建了一座金丝楠木大殿——澹泊敬诚殿。那笔者也曾去过，只是无论是木材的大小，还是殿宇的规模，都要小很多。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262566444" data-seq="262566445" data-pid="262566444" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262566444.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/42/A5/wKgBZ1n8j8mAcQdsAAln5FUMUCU24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/42/A5/wKgBZ1n8j8mAcQdsAAln5FUMUCU24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262566444" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_262569340" data-seq="262569341" data-pid="262569340" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262569340.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/44/95/wKgBZ1n8k2KAPHPyAA0oM8lto4412.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/44/95/wKgBZ1n8k2KAPHPyAA0oM8lto4412.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262569340" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_263828026" data-seq="263828027" data-pid="263828026" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/263828026.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F2/B9/wKgBZ1oCcaaAUWmRAAmvP_EWqoI55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F2/B9/wKgBZ1oCcaaAUWmRAAmvP_EWqoI55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="263828026" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="261976978">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;要论木材的稀有程度，只有慈禧定东陵里的黄花梨木大殿可以与长陵大殿相媲美，但规格较小。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262571237" data-seq="262571238" data-pid="262571237" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7903705/262571237.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/45/8D/wKgBZ1n8lbOAPNk2AAqejsFpFCU52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/45/8D/wKgBZ1n8lbOAPNk2AAqejsFpFCU52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262571237" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262575894">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;过了祾恩殿往里走，就是棂星门，再往后是一个城楼，名叫宝城。
        </p>
    
</div>
